# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas10.rpy:14
translate chinese danas10_fc8209c6:

    # cw "It's okay, I guess."
    cw "这样也行吧。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas10.rpy:16
translate chinese danas10_ceeea1c4:

    # cw "I think I'd rather live somewhere bigger, like Whiterock, or Baltimore, or something."
    cw "我觉得我还是想住个更大的地方，比如怀特洛克，或者巴尔的摩之类的。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas10.rpy:17
translate chinese danas10_be887bf3:

    # cw "There's just not much to do here. It gets a little boring sometimes."
    cw "这里实在没什么好玩的。 有时候确实有点无聊。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas10.rpy:19
translate chinese danas10_c3a79c9e:

    # cw "And for such a small place, you'd think the crime rate would be better, but it's really not."
    cw "而且这么个小地方，本以为犯罪率会低些，结果其实不然。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas10.rpy:20
translate chinese danas10_193b3ada:

    # cw "Seems like there's drugs on every street corner here."
    cw "感觉这里的每个街角都有毒品。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas10.rpy:22
translate chinese danas10_a557b394:

    # cw "But it's not too bad, I guess."
    cw "不过，我想情况也没那么糟。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas10.rpy:24
translate chinese danas10_957542dd:

    # cw "I can't really see myself moving, unless there was a really good opportunity somewhere else..."
    cw "我实在没法想象自己搬走，除非别处有特别好的机会……"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas10.rpy:26
translate chinese danas10_7a92643a:

    # cw "... or if Terry had to move for work or something."
    cw "……或者特里因为工作之类的原因必须搬走。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas10.rpy:28
translate chinese danas10_23b19054:

    # cw "But I don't think that's going to happen any time soon."
    cw "不过我觉得短期内不会发生这种事。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas10.rpy:30
translate chinese danas10_b627e713:

    # cw "It has you."
    cw "毕竟你还在这里。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas10.rpy:32
translate chinese danas10_7272bb00:

    # cw "And Skyhill is growing. They're opening up new places all the time."
    cw "而且斯凯希尔正在发展。他们一直在开新店。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas10.rpy:33
translate chinese danas10_32c7b850:

    # cw "So maybe it won't always be so boring."
    cw "所以也许以后不会一直这么无聊。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas10.rpy:36
translate chinese danas10_5ce59e29:

    # cw "Not that I really get out much anyway."
    cw "反正我平时也没怎么出门。"

